<div style="max-width: 560px; padding: 20px; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 5px; margin: 40px auto; font-family: Open Sans,Helvetica,Arial; font-size: 15px; color: #666;">
<div style="color: #444444; font-weight: normal;">
<div style="text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 26px; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: solid 3px #eeeeee;">{site_name}</div>
<div>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;">Hello, again! Welcome to Showcase India. We are so thrilled to have you be a part of our global community of talent.</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;">Your account is now active and you can get started on creating your showcase by clicking on the button below.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="padding: 0 30px 30px 30px; border-bottom: 3px solid #eeeeee;">
<div style="padding: 10px 0 50px 0; text-align: center;"><a style="background: #555555; color: #fff; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 3px; letter-spacing: 0.3px;" href="{login_url}">Create My Showcase</a></div>
<div style="padding: 10px 0px 50px; text-align: left;">At the heart of Showcase India lies the experience and tenacity of fellow creative souls. We are a community of professionals that are passionate about showcasing talent in India in the best and most efficient way possible. Please do not hesitate to reach out to us on support@showcaseindia.com for any trouble you may be having, any questions you may have or even if you just want to say hello! We want to hear from you!</div>
<div style="padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 50px; text-align: left;">Let’s get started on our journey together.</div>
</div>
<div style="color: #999; padding: 20px 30px;">
<div>Thank you,</div>
<div>Team <a style="color: #3ba1da; text-decoration: none;" href="{site_url}">{site_name}</a> </div>
</div>
</div>